    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skin on) into discs</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic clove[s] </strong>open by squashing with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Top, tail and chop your<strong> carrot[s] </strong>into rounds</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
