    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>crushed garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>carrot rounds</strong> to the dish</p><p>Add in your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>with your<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>then bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>beef & bacon mix</strong></p>",
